                        code.highlighter-rouge &lt;h6&gt;&lt;/h6&gt;
                td
                    span.h6 h6. Bootstrap heading
    h2#lists Lists
    p
        | All lists—
        code.highlighter-rouge &lt;ul&gt;
        | , 
        code.highlighter-rouge &lt;ol&gt;
        | , and 
        code.highlighter-rouge &lt;dl&gt;
        | —have their 
        code.highlighter-rouge margin-top
        |  removed and a 
        code.highlighter-rouge margin-bottom: 1rem
        | . Nested lists have no 
        code.highlighter-rouge margin-bottom
        | .
    .bd-example
        ul
            li Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet
            li Consectetur adipiscing elit
            li Integer molestie lorem at massa
            li Facilisis in pretium nisl aliquet
            li
                | Nulla volutpat aliquam velit
                ul
                    li Phasellus iaculis neque
                    li Purus sodales ultricies
                    li Vestibulum laoreet porttitor sem
                    li Ac tristique libero volutpat at
            li Faucibus porta lacus fringilla vel
            li Aenean sit amet erat nunc
            li Eget porttitor lorem
        ol
            li Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet
            li Consectetur adipiscing elit
            li Integer molestie lorem at massa
            li Facilisis in pretium nisl aliquet
            li Nulla volutpat aliquam velit
            li Faucibus porta lacus fringilla vel
            li Aenean sit amet erat nunc
            li Eget porttitor lorem
    p
        | For simpler styling, clear hierarchy, and better spacing, description lists have updated 
        code.highlighter-rouge margin
        | s. 
        code.highlighter-rouge &lt;dd&gt;
        | s reset 
        code.highlighter-rouge margin-left
        |  to 
        code.highlighter-rouge 0
        |  and add 
        code.highlighter-rouge margin-bottom: .5rem
        | . 
        code.highlighter-rouge &lt;dt&gt;
        | s are 
        strong bolded
        | .
    .bd-example
        dl
            dt Description lists
            dd A description list is perfect for defining terms.
            dt Euismod
            dd Vestibulum id ligula porta felis euismod semper eget lacinia odio sem.
            dd Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus.
            dt Malesuada porta
            dd Etiam porta sem malesuada magna mollis euismod.
    h2#preformatted-text Preformatted text
    p
        | The 
        code.highlighter-rouge &lt;pre&gt;
        |  element is reset to remove its 
        code.highlighter-rouge margin-top
        |  and use 
        code.highlighter-rouge rem
        |  units for its 
        code.highlighter-rouge margin-bottom
        | .
    .bd-example
        pre.
            \n.example-element {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            }
    h2#tables Tables
    p
        | Tables are slightly adjusted to style 
        code.highlighter-rouge &lt;caption&gt;
        | s, collapse borders, and ensure consistent 
        code.highlighter-rouge text-align
        |  throughout. Additional changes for borders, padding, and more come with 
        a(href='/docs/content/tables/')
            | the 
            code.highlighter-rouge .table
            |  class
        | .
    .bd-example
        table
            caption
                | This is an example table, and this is its caption to describe the contents.
            thead
                tr
                    th Table heading
                    th Table heading
